    <DocSection Title="Features">
        <TailCard>
            <ChildContent>
                <div style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">
                    <ul class="space-y-2" style="list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem;">
                        <li><strong>Layout Options:</strong> Horizontal and vertical layouts</li>
                        <li><strong>Spacing Control:</strong> None, Small, Medium, Large spacing options</li>
                        <li><strong>Size Variants:</strong> Xs, Sm, Md, Lg, Xl size options</li>
                        <li><strong>Border Radius:</strong> None, Small, Medium, Large, Full (pill) radius options</li>
                        <li><strong>Attached Mode:</strong> Seamless connected buttons with shared borders</li>
                        <li><strong>Separated Mode:</strong> Individual buttons with spacing</li>
                        <li><strong>Border Support:</strong> Optional border around the entire group</li>
                        <li><strong>Shadow Effects:</strong> Optional shadow for depth</li>
                        <li><strong>Mixed Variants:</strong> Support for different button variants in same group</li>
                        <li><strong>Icon Support:</strong> Works with buttons that have icons</li>
                        <li><strong>Theme Support:</strong> Full CSS variable integration for seamless theming</li>
                        <li><strong>Hover Effects:</strong> Proper z-index handling for attached buttons</li>
                        <li><strong>Focus States:</strong> Accessible focus indicators</li>
                        <li><strong>Dark Mode:</strong> Automatic dark mode support</li>
                        <li><strong>Lightweight:</strong> Only ~4 KB in size</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </ChildContent>
        </TailCard>
    </DocSection>

    <DocSection Title="Accessibility">
        <TailCard>
            <ChildContent>
                <div style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">
                    <p class="mb-4">TailButtonGroup is built with accessibility in mind:</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2" style="list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem;">
                        <li>Maintains proper button semantics for all child buttons</li>
                        <li>Keyboard accessible - all buttons remain fully navigable</li>
                        <li>Proper z-index management for attached buttons on hover/focus</li>
                        <li>Visible focus indicators with proper contrast</li>
                        <li>Screen reader friendly - no additional ARIA needed</li>
                        <li>High contrast ratios for all states</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </ChildContent>
        </TailCard>
    </DocSection>
